      "text": [
        "4293 - وَ عَنِ اَلرَّجُلِ يَحْلِفُ لِصَاحِبِ اَلْعُشُورِ يُحْرِزُ بِذَلِكَ مَالَهُ قَالَ \"نَعَمْ\"."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.4293 - And regarding a man who swears an oath to the tax collector in order to protect his wealth.\nImam (as) said: \"Yes.\""
        ]
      }
    }
